Amazon Alexa and the Walton Smart appliance home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off air conditioner. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your air conditioner setting - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 

After connecting Alexa to your walton smart appliance products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "walton smart appliance" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one walton smart appliance account in our "walton smart appliance" app;
(3). You need to have some walton smart appliance devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “walton smart appliance" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "walton smart appliance" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "walton smart appliance" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "walton smart appliance", and you'll be navigated to our login page;
(9). Input your walton smart appliance account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on air conditioner"
“Alexa, turn off air conditioner"
“Alexa, set the air conditioner to heat"
